text: Elizabeth Anne Greene (born May 1, 2003) is an American actress. She played Dawn Harper in the Nickelodeon show Nicky, Ricky, Dicky & Dawn from 2014 to 2018. She has been playing Sophie Dixon in the ABC family drama A Million Little Things since 2018. == References == Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Dallas Category:American child actors Category:American television actors
